        "subject": "LU-9198 lfsck: handle LCME_FL_INIT flag",
        "message": "LU-9198 lfsck: handle LCME_FL_INIT flag\n\nFor PFL file, if we allocate OST-object(s) for the component,\nthen related lov_comp_md_entry_v1::lcme_flags will be marked\nwith the flag LCME_FL_INIT. Otherwise if without such flag,\nit means we have not allocate OST-obejcts for the component.\nThe layout LFSCK needs to handle such flag properly.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I563e7135e8256dfb921ab03dd8338e8320798186\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/pfl"
    }
